<Layout
title="Boka tandemflyg hos Skysport i Åre"
description="Welcome to Rico's portfolio site! Explore my work as a web/UI designer with 8+ years of experience in creating captivating visuals and interactive experiences."
keywords="Tandemflyg, Paragliding, Åre"
><Topper />
    <div class=" py-8 px-4 sm:px-8  md:px-68   dark:text-slate-200">
      <Breadcrumbs linkTextFormat="capitalized" separatorAriaHidden={false} customizeLinks={customLastPart}>
